722
00:50:23,353 --> 00:50:25,355
They also want an increase
in their basic pay

723
00:50:25,439 --> 00:50:27,983
and seniority allowance
based on the years of experience.

724
00:50:28,775 --> 00:50:31,319
Seoul Office of Education
agrees with the need of change,

725
00:50:31,403 --> 00:50:33,196
but they're showing different opinions.

