Do you know a first-grader
named Kang Pil-gu?

728
00:50:48,086 --> 00:50:49,671
Do you guys know him?

729
00:50:50,047 --> 00:50:51,173
He got transferred here.

730
00:50:51,256 --> 00:50:53,925
-You mean Pickled Radish?
-He's probably in the cafeteria.

731
00:50:54,217 --> 00:50:55,343
"Pickled Radish"?

732
00:51:04,644 --> 00:51:07,230
Doesn't your uncle
live in Elegance Palace?

733
00:51:07,898 --> 00:51:09,274
He lives with his uncle?

734
00:51:09,775 --> 00:51:11,777
What's with your lunch
when you live there?

735
00:51:19,534 --> 00:51:21,203
He apparently likes pickled radish.

736
00:51:23,121 --> 00:51:25,123
I'm the best baseball player
among all of us.

737
00:51:25,665 --> 00:51:28,293
Who cares what I eat?
I just need to join the Major League.

738
00:51:28,460 --> 00:51:31,338
He even eats cup noodles
at the convenience store.

739
00:51:31,546 --> 00:51:32,964
His mom must be really nice.

740
00:51:37,552 --> 00:51:41,556
I had never seen my mom so angry before.

741
00:51:44,309 --> 00:51:46,353
YEOKJAM ELEMENTARY SCHOOL

742
00:51:47,312 --> 00:51:49,773
Back then, I thought she was angry.

743
00:51:51,483 --> 00:51:52,526
Get up.

744
00:51:55,821 --> 00:51:58,156
-Get up.
-Why?

745
00:51:59,241 --> 00:52:00,575
I don't want to go.

746
00:52:04,162 --> 00:52:06,039
I don't want to go!

747
00:52:06,289 --> 00:52:07,582
I'm not going to go!

748
00:52:07,666 --> 00:52:10,460
But now that I think about it,
she was just sad.

749
00:52:10,544 --> 00:52:11,837
I have training!

750
00:52:11,920 --> 00:52:13,463
What's with you all of a sudden?

751
00:52:14,047 --> 00:52:15,465
Are you going to live here?

752
00:52:15,549 --> 00:52:16,466
Is there a problem?

753
00:52:16,550 --> 00:52:18,552
I said I'm going to join
the Major League!

754
00:52:18,635 --> 00:52:21,263
I want you to choose
between me and the Major League.

755
00:52:21,346 --> 00:52:22,931
Why would you ask me to choose?

756
00:52:23,723 --> 00:52:26,560
Pil-gu, I don't need you to become
an MLB player.

757
00:52:27,018 --> 00:52:29,312
I would never swap you for Ryu Hyun-jin.

758
00:52:29,396 --> 00:52:30,689
So I want you to choose.

759
00:52:31,022 --> 00:52:33,108
Is it me or the Major League? Tell me.

760
00:52:33,441 --> 00:52:35,944
-What do you want?
-Why won't you answer my question?

761
00:52:48,290 --> 00:52:49,749
What's the matter with you?

762
00:52:49,833 --> 00:52:52,294
Why do you keep walking on eggshells?

763
00:52:52,377 --> 00:52:53,837
Why can't you be honest with me?

764
00:52:54,129 --> 00:52:57,132
Who told you to walk on eggshells
and be shy about speaking up?

765
00:52:57,215 --> 00:52:59,467
If you keep this up,
I'm not going to be your mom!

766
00:52:59,551 --> 00:53:01,887
I might as well just leave!
I'll go ahead and leave!

767
00:53:02,387 --> 00:53:05,765
